k ages of=\r\n Kali yuga, rational minds wouldn&#39;t accept anything that didn&#39;t &quot;make sense=\r\n&quot;. Being established in Self became an unnatural, ridiculous and incomprehe=\r\nnsible notion. So the &quot;spirit of comprehension&quot; (Mercury) became relevant. =\r\nAn avatara corresponding to Mercury occurred and tried to explain being est=\r\nablished in Self as a comprehensible notion, so that rational minds of that=\r\n age would accept it to an extent and attempt it.\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;Avataras o=\r\nccur based on the needs of collective consciousness. Of course, if one&#39;s co=\r\nnsciousness is in a different state from the collective consciousness of th=\r\nat time, the current avatara may not be relevant to one.\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;*=\r\n=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0 *=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=\r\n=C2=A0=C2=A0 *\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; I respect Rama, but I worship Krshna.\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;=\r\n=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;I am\n awestruck by Krishna and worship him, but I see Rama as an=\r\n ideal that I MAY be able to emulate oneday. In fact, I recommend the appro=\r\nach to others.\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;Though I said Rama and Krishna are almost the=\r\n same, there is a difference between soul and perfected mind. Soul is a spa=\r\nrk of Shiva and a perfected mind is a spark of Chit Shakti (whereas an impe=\r\nrfect mind is a spark of Maya shakti).\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;Best regards, Na=\r\nrasimha -------- Astrology & Spirituality Resources: http://www.vedicastrol=\r\noger.org/\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;--------\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;=C2=A0\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;From: rajarshi nandy &lt;rajarshi14@yaho=\r\no.co.in&gt;\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;To: &quot;vedic-wisdom@yahoogroups.com&quot; &lt;vedic-wisdom@yahoogroups.=\r\ncom&gt; \n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;Sent: Sunday, May 5, 2013 3:34 AM\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;Subject: Re: [vedic-wisdo=